name: 本尼特·邓恩
introduction: Bennett Dunn had an early interest in music and entertainment. He started piano in the 1st grade, then took up drums, then guitar, then highland bagpipes, then Irish tin whistle, then the Irish Uilleann pipes.He is known for his critically-acclaimed portrayal of Buddy in The Buddy Holly Story, appearing regionally and in a North American Tour. He has also appeared in movies, television and commercials.Bennett is on leave from the entertainment industry, pursuing his other deep passions of life: raising a family and exploring the field of science and engineering.
